        <pb xml:id="F34790185" n="1" facs="https://cdm17313.contentdm.oclc.org/iiif/2/mdah:47131/full/full/0/default.jpg"/>
        <div xml:id="OTP34790185">
        <fw type="pageNum">Page 1</fw>
          <p corresp='TTP34790185P0' xml:id='OTP34790185P0'>Salem City Sebastian Co .Ark
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34790185P1' xml:id='OTP34790185P1'>October 3<add place='above'><hi rend='underline'>rd</hi><sub>,,</sub></add> 1878
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34790185P2' xml:id='OTP34790185P2'>Governor of Mississippi
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34790185P3' xml:id='OTP34790185P3'>His Excellency would be pleased to know if there is a <rs ref='#S32065746'>reward</rs> offered for the <rs ref='#S62954'>arrest</rs> of one <rs ref='#S32074398'>William Bates</rs> if this statement be correct His Excellency would be pleased to <del rend='overstrike'>  know if there is A</del> get full description of <rs ref='#S63926'>murder</rs> information would be thankfully [Read?]
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34790185P4' xml:id='OTP34790185P4'>Vary Respectfull<lb/>
<rs ref='#S32181748'>F,, J,, Eastman</rs>
</p>


        </div>
        <pb xml:id="F34790186" n="2" facs="https://cdm17313.contentdm.oclc.org/iiif/2/mdah:47132/full/full/0/default.jpg"/>
        <div xml:id="OTP34790186">
        <fw type="pageNum">Page 2</fw>
          <p corresp='TTP34790186P0' xml:id='OTP34790186P0'>Arkansas (Examine again)<lb/>
<hr/><lb/>
<b>EXECUTIVE OFFICE,</b>
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34790186P1' xml:id='OTP34790186P1'><b>STATE OF MISSISSIPPI,</b><lb/>
F. J. Eastman County,<lb/>
<hr/><lb/>
From [gap] <lb/>
Address Salem City Ark<lb/>
Dated Octo. 3<add place='above'>rd</add>. 1878<lb/>
Received [gap] <lb/>
Answered Octo 13<add place='above'>th</add>. 1878<lb/>
<hr/><lb/>
SUBJECT
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34790186P2' xml:id='OTP34790186P2'>Asks if there is a Reward for <hi rend='underline'>William Bates</hi><lb/>
(Examine further)
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34790186P3' xml:id='OTP34790186P3'>(Inclosures [gap])<lb/>
<hr/><lb/>
<b>J. M. STONE,</b>
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34790186P4' xml:id='OTP34790186P4'>Governor.<lb/>
<del rend='overstrike'><b>KINLOCH FALCONER</b></del> ^ A. M. Nelson^
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34790186P5' xml:id='OTP34790186P5'>Private Secretary.<lb/>
<hr/>
</p>


        </div>
  </body>
